column1: Cum Town Farewell<p><a href="https://www.patreon.com/posts/cum-town-123539704" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">march 3
column2: 2025</a></p><p>Hello to anyone that's forgotten to cancel!</p><p>Long overdue
column3: here's the final episode of Cum Town.</p><p>The show has often been accused of being "ironic." So I want to be clear when I say
column5: thanks to everyone that ever listened (and hopefully laughed.)</p><p>In 2016
column6: we sat down and recorded an hour of audio in Stav's apartment
column7: just going through the motions of what was required of comedians that year. Okay
column9: I guess we have to have a podcast now. We didn't have a name for the show. We didn't know if we'd do a second episode. </p><p>What grew out of it changed our lives in ways we didn't think were possible. Playstation
column11: harassing Japanese people - in JAPAN! And it wouldn't have happened without your support. </p><p>So now
column12: that our journey has come to an end
column13: we'd like to say to the fans
column15: the reddit psychos, the bees, the guy that did heroin on stream, the goth latinos, smalldickproblems, the tinder update guy, and everyone else, thank you and godspeed. Farewell. </p><p>Love,</p><p>Nick, Stav, and Adam.</p>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 01:49:25 GMThttps://s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/podcast.blakeslee.uk/ct/731-cum-town-farewell.mp3
